OL,4,G1800FPolice Interceptors
OL,5,     GDuncan receives a shock when a
OL,6,     Gcyclist who has been crushed and
OL,7,     Gtrapped under a car turns out to
OL,8,     Gbe someone he knows.
OL,9,G1900FPolice Interceptors
OL,10,     GCumbria's interceptor teams are
OL,11,     Gcalled out to deal with a
OL,12,     Gsuspected gunman, a pedestrian
OL,13,     Gunder a car and to destroy a
OL,14,     Gcannabis farm.
OL,15,G2000FMotorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,16,     FSpeeders
OL,17,     GCases include a driver without a
OL,18,     Glicence whose car reeks of
OL,19,     Gcannabis, a man who can't spell
OL,20,     Gthe name he gives to officers,
OL,21,     Gand boy racers causing car park
OL,22,     Gchaos.
